title: Burning Greens Vegetarian Enterprise
description: Stocks healthy vegetarian products such as vege-analogues, chilled taho, and soy milk. Organic skin and herbal supplements also available. Distributor of products from Nature's Way USA, and skin care products from Human Nature natural beauty products. Free lecture events and demos. Note: food service stopped in May 2011.
streetAddress: Lot 3 Blk 4, Corrina Ave, Pasong Tamo, Quezon City
